rows.label: campfev11_500_110_msg0001
rows.name: Finally, we set out for the city...

rows.label: campfev11_500_110_msg0002
rows.name: Let's hope it's worth the wait.

rows.label: campfev11_500_110_msg0003
rows.name:
Ooh, I can't wait to find out what
kind of place it is!

rows.label: campfev11_500_110_msg0004
rows.name:
Kasumi. Remember, this isn't a
sightseeing expedition.

rows.label: campfev11_500_110_msg0006
rows.name:
But surely there will be a bit of
spare time for me and Laura-sama
to go shopping..

rows.label: campfev11_500_110_msg0007
rows.name:
I didn't mean to wag my finger
at you Kasumi

rows.label: campfev11_500_110_msg0008
rows.name:
Of course, you're the only one that
can do that stuff with Laura

rows.label: campfev11_500_110_msg0009
rows.name:
If you can get away with it,
more power to you.

rows.label: campfev11_500_110_msg0011
rows.name:
You should come too. We're going to
need someone to carry all the things
we buy.

rows.label: campfev11_500_110_msg0012
rows.name:
Well...all right. I did kinda want
some new shoes, anyway...
